# AVD-KSV-0017 / readOnlyRootFilesystem: The frontend (Nuxt/Nitro) writes
# temporary files to the container filesystem at runtime. The container runs
# as non-root with all capabilities dropped and seccomp RuntimeDefault applied.
AVD-KSV-0017

# AVD-KSV-0036 / sensitive ConfigMap keys: NITRO_PORT is a TCP port number,
# not a secret. Trivy's heuristic flags it based on the "PORT" substring —
# false positive for a non-sensitive configuration value.
AVD-KSV-0036
